eat, and COâ‚‚.</p>\n\n<h2>Upcoming events</h2>\n<ul style=\"list-style:none; padding-left:0; margin:0;\">\n<li style=\"margin-bottom:20px; line-height:1.4;\">\n1-4 March 2026: Visit University of East Anglia, Norwich.\n<li style=\"margin-bottom:20px; line-height:1.4;\">\n21-28 February 2026: Ocean Science Meeting, Glasgow. Looking forward to catching up.\n<h2>Recent Updates</h2>\n<ul style=\"list-style:none; padding-left:0; margin:0;\">\n<li style=\"margin-bottom:20px; line-height:1.4;\">\nFebruary 2026: MSCA Postdoctoral Fellowship 2025: scored 96.6 (grant 96.8) â€“ on the reserve list, disappointing, yet still smiling with the Seal of Excellence ðŸ˜„\n</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom:20px; line-height:1.4;\">\nFebruary 2026: Selected to co-chair the SOLAS Early Career Scientist Committee (ECSC) for 2026-2028\n</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom:20px; line-height:1.4;\">\nJanuary 2026: Invited to be an editor of the EGU journal *Earth Observation*\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"flex:1; position:absolute; top:-480px; right:-370px; text-align:left;\">\n<img src=\"Photo.png\" alt=\"My Photo\" style=\"width:120px; border-radius:0%; margin-bottom:15px; margin-left:20px;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:17px; line-height:1.65;\">\n<p><strong>ECR in Marine Science</strong></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top:-10px; margin-bottom:30px; padding-left:20px;\">\n<li>Air-sea gas exchange</li>\n<li>Ocean carbon cycle</li>\n<li>Eddy covariance</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Contact</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:-10px;\">RD 2 - Chemical Oceanography<br>\nGEOMAR Helmholtz Centre for Ocean Research Kiel,<br>\nWischhofstraÃŸe 1-3, 24148 Kiel<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:ydong@geomar.de\">ydong@geomar.de</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":tru